   <br></br>
   <h1>GoogImager</h1>
<font size="3">(Items in <font color="blue">blue</font> are new
to the Google
Image
Search
through GoogImager)</font>
   <br></br>
<p>GoogImager is a small utility for making a query to the Google Image
Search using parameters of Google Advanced Search and some exclusive
parameters.</p>
<p>GoogImager features:</p>
<p>Specify Logic Conditions</p>
<p>Include/<font color="blue">exclude</font> certain domains in an image
search</p>
<p>Search for specific type of file: .jpg, 
<font color="blue">.jpeg
</font>, .gif</p>
<p>Set the number of results per page, and 
<font color="blue">which page to view for the
search result
</font></p>
<p><font color="blue">"History of queries" for repeating previous searches
with restoring all parameters of searching</font></p>
<p><font color="blue">Search for images in non-English language</font></p>
<p><font color="blue">Search for images, as well as text documents and
google topic-specific
searches, such as documents concerning Linux, Macintosh, and the
Government</font></p><br>
